data.name: Pumpkin Seed Pesto
data.quickTastyDescription: A vibrant and nutty twist on traditional pesto, perfect for pasta or as a spread!
detailedCookingInstructions: Toast pumpkin seeds in a dry skillet over medium heat until golden (optional).
In a food processor, combine pumpkin seeds, fresh basil, garlic, and Parmesan cheese.
Pulse until finely chopped, scraping down the sides as needed.
With the processor running, slowly add olive oil until well blended.
Add lemon juice and salt, and pulse again to combine.
data.detailedName: Simple and Nutty Pumpkin Seed Pesto
data.modifiersForBase: Using pumpkin seeds instead of traditional pine nuts
